definitions.definition: Ellipsis of Woodstock Festival , an American rock music festival originally held in 1969 in New York state near Woodstock ; ( by extension ) a large, influential gathering .

subdefinitions.definition: A place in Australia : A village in Cowra Shire, New South Wales . A rural community in the City of Townsville , Queensland . A rural locality in Huon Valley council area, Tasmania . A locality in the City of Whittlesea , Victoria .
A place in New Zealand : A small settlement south of Motueka , Tasman district, New Zealand . A small settlement near Kaniere and Hokitika , West Coast region, New Zealand .
A suburb of Cape Town , South Africa .

A place in Canada : A town and parish in Carleton County , New Brunswick . A town in Newfoundland , Newfoundland and Labrador . A community in Yarmouth district municipality, Yarmouth County , Nova Scotia . A city , the seat of Oxford County , Ontario .

A place in the United Kingdom : A suburb of Kingswood and ward in South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire , England ( OS grid ref ST6573 ) . A settlement in Tunstall parish, Swale district, Kent , England ( OS grid ref TQ9060 ) . A market town and civil parish with a town council in West Oxfordshire district, Oxfordshire , England ( OS grid ref SP4416 ) . A small village in Ambleston community, Pembrokeshire , Wales ( OS grid ref SN0225 ) .

A place in the United States : A town in Bibb County and Tuscaloosa County , Alabama . A neighbourhood of Alameda , Alameda County , California . A town in Windham County , Connecticut . A city in Cherokee County , Georgia . A city , the county seat of McHenry County , Illinois . A township in Schuyler County , Illinois . A town in Oxford County , Maine . An unincorporated community in Howard County , Maryland . A township in Lenawee County , Michigan . A minor city in Pipestone County , Minnesota . A town in Grafton County , New Hampshire . A town and census-designated place therein, in Ulster County , New York . A neighborhood of the Bronx , New York . A village in Rush Township, Champaign County , Ohio . A neighbourhood in south-east Portland , Oregon . A town , the shire town of Windsor County , Vermont . A town , the county seat of Shenandoah County , Virginia . An unincorporated community in Northampton County , Virginia . An unincorporated community in the town of Henrietta , Richland County , Wisconsin .

main_definition: ( music ) Ellipsis of Woodstock Festival , an American rock music festival originally held in 1969 in New York state near Woodstock ; ( by extension ) a large, influential gathering .
